metadata.name: Yrneha Tamlyranth
metadata.attribstrtext: You are stronger than most human.
metadata.attribdextext: You are more agile than most human.
metadata.alignmenttext: You tend to have no respect for rules, other people's lives, or anything but your own desires, which are typically selfish and cruel. You set a high value on personal freedom, but do not have much regard for the lives or freedom of other people. You do not work well in groups because you resent being given orders and usually do not behave yourself unless there is no alternative.
